item.title: CVE-2022-3605|2024-08-03T01:14:02.026Z -- unknown -- wp%20csv%20exporter
item.description: The WP CSV Exporter WordPress plugin before 1.3.7 does not properly escape the fields when exporting data as CSV, leading to a CSV injection vulnerability.

item.title: CVE-2022-3249|2024-08-03T01:07:05.559Z -- unknown -- wp%20csv%20exporter
item.description: The WP CSV Exporter WordPress plugin before 1.3.7 does not properly sanitise and escape some parameters before using them in a SQL statement, allowing high privilege users such as admin to perform SQL injection attacks
